        "setup": "In the Azure portal, open your Batch account and retrieve one of the account access keys from the account settings described in [Manage Batch accounts](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/batch/accounts). The Batch REST auth doc states the Batch service supports authentication via Shared Key; use your Batch account name together with one of its access keys to sign requests.",
